ProtoResult:
. "The series $\sum ^\infty_{n=k} a_nb_n$ converges if 
   $\lim_{n\to\infty} a_n= 0$ $ \sum |a_{n+1}-a_n|<\infty, $ 
   and $ |b_k+b_{k+1}+\cdots+b_n|\le M, n\ge k, $ for some 
   constant $M$"
